snippet.title: My Baby Unicorn - Pony Care 🦄🌟 Cuteness, Magic & Fun for Kids! | TutoTOONS
snippet.description:
Become the best horse and pony nanny with a fun #MyBabyUnicorn game 🦄 ▼ Download #MyBabyUnicornGame​ for free! ▼
https://tutotoons.com/games/details/467
Official My Baby Unicorn Trailer 🌈 ▶▶▶ https://youtu.be/ZUN5CgWUeAk

Watch more fun family friendly​​​​ videos from #TutoTOONS ▶▶▶ https://www.youtube.com/c/TutoTOONSOfficial/videos

---
Become the best horse and pony nanny with fun My Baby Unicorn game for girls and boys, kids and toddlers! Hatch a colorful egg and take care of the cutest newborn unicorn with rainbow hair! Bathe, feed, potty train, dress up, sing to sleep and play fun games with your tiny virtual unicorn friend! Check the stats and watch your magical pony pet and its amazing rainbow hair grow! Decorate the baby unicorn’s room with rainbow colors! Become the best newborn horse and pony babysitter!

HATCH AN EGG & DRESS UP YOUR NEWBORN UNICORN!
Surprise! You have a magical egg to hatch! Take care of it and watch a tiny baby unicorn hatch! Now you are a magical horse and pony babysitter! Take good care of the newborn unicorn! Design and decorate the baby’s room with rainbow colors and fun accessories! Dress up your baby unicorn in colorful outfits for babies, toddlers and kids!

BATHE & POTTY TRAIN YOUR TINY UNICORN!
Your baby unicorn wants to be super clean! Bathe the little one and watch the magical pony’s fun reactions to rainbow soap, slime bath, super hot and ice cold water! Time to potty train your tiny unicorn pet! Don’t forget to wash the hands!

FEED & SING TO SLEEP YOUR BABY PONY!
Feed your baby unicorn with fun and yummy foods: fruits, veggies, candy, donuts and even a cute unicorn cake! Give a squishy toy for kids to your baby unicorn friend and sing the little one to sleep! Sweet dreams, baby unicorn!

PLAY GAMES WITH YOUR RAINBOW UNICORN FRIEND!
Take good care of your magical pony pet and unlock new fun mini games every day! Play memory, coloring and decoration games with your virtual unicorn! Jump on clouds, slide down a rainbow and enjoy more surprise games for girls and boys, kids and toddlers! Unbox squishy collectible unicorn toys for kids!

---
